Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.269 --> 00:00:05.739 line:0%
 
AND THE BRITISH ARE TEARING
THROUGH THE COLONIES.

00:00:05.739 --> 00:00:07.140 line:0%
 
BLAP, BLAP.

00:00:07.140 --> 00:00:09.142 line:0%
 
KGGH!

00:00:09.142 --> 00:00:12.346 line:0%
 
SYBIL LUDINGTON
JUST HAD HER 16TH BIRTHDAY.

00:00:12.346 --> 00:00:16.583 line:0%
 
HER DAD, HENRY LUDINGTON, IS
THE HEAD OF THE LOCAL MILITIA,

00:00:16.583 --> 00:00:18.886 line:0%
 
FENDING OFF THE BRITISH.

00:00:18.886 --> 00:00:23.457
SO ON THIS PARTICULAR NIGHT,
SHE'S TUCKING IN HER BROTHERS

00:00:23.457 --> 00:00:25.259
AND SISTERS,
AND ALL OF A SUDDEN,

00:00:25.259 --> 00:00:26.994
KA-KA, KA-KA.

00:00:26.994 --> 00:00:28.929
THERE'S A KNOCK ON THE DOOR.

00:00:28.929 --> 00:00:32.065
THIS MAN IS AT THE DOOR--
OH, MY GOD.

00:00:32.065 --> 00:00:33.400
HE'S SO OUT OF BREATH.

00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:37.905
THE BRITISH ARE BURNING
DANBURY, CONNECTICUT.

00:00:39.706 --> 00:00:42.743
OKAY. OKAY,
SO HENRY LUDINGTON IS LIKE,

00:00:42.743 --> 00:00:46.146
I NEED TO GO KNOCK
ON EVERY DOOR,

00:00:46.146 --> 00:00:50.784
GET OUR MILITIA,
AND SAVE OUR COUNTRY.

00:00:50.784 --> 00:00:52.686
WELL, HERE'S THE THING THOUGH.

00:00:52.686 --> 00:00:56.023
I HAVE TO STAY HERE TO,
LIKE, RALLY THE TROOPS,

00:00:56.023 --> 00:00:57.758
AND MAKE THE PLAN.

00:00:57.758 --> 00:01:00.327
IT'S NOT LIKE YOU CAN
SEND AN E-VITE OUT.

00:01:00.327 --> 00:01:03.864
SO WHO'S GONNA DO IT?

00:01:03.864 --> 00:01:08.669
I'LL DO IT,
COMES A PEEP FROM THE NIGHT.

00:01:08.669 --> 00:01:11.071
HEY.

00:01:11.071 --> 00:01:12.873
BLAH BLAH.

00:01:12.873 --> 00:01:14.408
I GOT IT.

00:01:14.408 --> 00:01:17.978
SYBIL COMES PEEP-PEEP-PEEPING
DOWN THE NIGHT,

00:01:17.978 --> 00:01:20.848
AND HER DAD'S LIKE,
SHE'S 16 YEARS OLD.

00:01:20.848 --> 00:01:22.382
SHE'S A GIRL.

00:01:22.382 --> 00:01:26.119
IT'S A [bleep]
HARD-ASS NIGHT OUTSIDE.

00:01:26.119 --> 00:01:29.723
