00:01:29.723 --> 00:01:32.359
WELL, [bleep].
WE DON'T HAVE A BETTER OPTION.

00:01:32.359 --> 00:01:36.296
SO YEAH,
WE'RE GONNA LET HER DO IT.

00:01:36.296 --> 00:01:38.098
